data.title: Desert Community Foundation
data.meta_description:
The Desert Community Foundation serves the cities of Palm Desert, Indian Wells, Rancho Mirage, La Quinta, Palm Springs, Indio, Cathedral City, Coachella, Mecca, Desert Hot Springs, Thousand Palms, Bermuda Dunes, & Thermal (Riverside Counties and the High and Low Deserts)

The Desert Community Foundation is a nonprofit organization that exists to oversee funds set up by members of our desert community and to make charitable grants to 501-c(3) organizations. Think of Community Foundations as pools of funds invested for the futures of our communities.
data.text:
OPEN A SCHOLARSHIP FUND WITH US

With over 20 years of managing scholarship programs for the finest private country clubs in the Coachella Valley, we're happy to share what we know.

(Bonus: Our Scholarship Funds come with our exclusive Advisory Committee formed with local educators, administrators and college specialists).
